---
title: Mexican-Inspired Chorizo Stew with Tortilla Chips
description: Packed with hearty and delicious chorizo and veggies, this Mexican stew is the perfect remedy to a long work week. Crushed tortilla chips and a dollop of sour cream offer a pop of flavour, perfect for finishing off this bowl of goodness.
